{"arkId":"cl010106829","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010106829","modified ":"2025-11-03","title":"Montre en forme de fleur","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre en forme de fleur"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1650","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 4","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1650,"imprecision":"","text":"1ere moiti\u00e9 du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Schultz, Michel","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 684","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre en forme de fleur ; bo\u00eetier en argent grav\u00e9 et amati en forme de bouton de fleur ovo\u00efde aux p\u00e9tales aux contours aigus press\u00e9s les uns contre les autres. Deux couvercles \u00e0 charni\u00e8re ; faces internes nervur\u00e9es et orn\u00e9es d\u0027arceaux se d\u00e9tachant sur fond amati. Pendant encadr\u00e9 de p\u00e9tales. Plaque du cadran grav\u00e9e de fleurs de fraisier, d\u0027une t\u00eate d\u0027ange et d\u0027un paysage au centre. Anneau horaire \u00e0 chiffres romains. Ajust\u00e9 dans le bo\u00eetier, mouvement \u00e0 \u00e9chappement \u00e0 verge, fus\u00e9e avec cha\u00eenette. Coq et cliquet reperc\u00e9s et grav\u00e9s de rinceaux fleuris. Piliers tourn\u00e9s en forme de balustre.\r\nMouvement sign\u00e9 : Michel Schultz \/ Dantzig.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Michel Schultz\/Dantzig","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,2","displayDimension":"5,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,2","displayDimension":"3,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,1","displayDimension":"2,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Dantzig = Danzig = Gdansk (Europe-\u003EPologne)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Alexandre-Charles Sauvageot (1781-1860) ; acquise en 1848, cf. le Livre d\u0027achat n\u00b0 2264 : \u0022Montre en argent, forme de fruit, du XVIe si\u00e8cle\u2026 70 francs\u0022 ; donation accept\u00e9e en 1856, acte notari\u00e9 le 6 mars 1857, n\u00b0 1364 : \u0022Montre en argent forme de coquillage, cadran dor\u00e9 et grav\u00e9, sign\u00e9 Michel Schulz Dantzig estim\u00e9e cent francs\u0022.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Sauvageot, Alexandre-Charles","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"donation","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de donation","value":"1856","startYear":1856,"endYear":1856}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"donation"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"},{"value":"Louis XIII (1610-1643)"}],"pla